{
  "stem": "311.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When something was going on, there were 10 of them, on each thing and all around when they-- when they were sending out or killing or-- or whatever they did, you know?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in the normal, like in the daytime, middle of the week-- usually, all those things happen on weekends.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, when they were taking to Treblinka or to wherever it is and killing people--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--most of that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the minute, you know, when I saw that-- And still, the ghetto, OK, I could get out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And once I was a little far out, I ripped it off.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to the movies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said to hell with you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, what I'm not supposed to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you-- you're supposed to be dehumanized.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You-- you're not supposed to have a telephone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You cannot ride the street car.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You cannot use the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You-- you're not supposed to go to the movies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] None of-- no, no, none of the entertainments.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the circus was still in town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had to go see it or whatever it is, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wouldn't miss it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't want to be a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I want to be the announcer in the circus.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The-- this was-- this was the type of kid I was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is this-- when I start-- when I-- when I start and you see that, then my head went-- then-- then-- then my father didn't know how to hold me anymore.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wanted to get out from that ghetto, so badly, and stay out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I saw it, this was still around 1942.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't kill you in front of you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took you out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and you never came back, you understand?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
